yingyinNormal.en: It doesn't matter whether he was unconscious or not, whether he lives or dies.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不论他是否意识清醒，不论他是死是活。

yingyinNormal.en: Let me remind you, ma'am, the president was unconscious when this investigation began.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要提醒你，女士，总统在这次调查开始前就已陷入昏迷……

yingyinNormal.en: I wonder if I've been experiencing physiological manifestations of some sort of unconscious emotional turmoil.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在想我是否正在经受由于无意识感情上混乱而导致的一些生理表现。

yingyinNormal.en: That show ended with all the residents of New York either dead or unconscious. Now I'll never know what happened.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这剧季末剧情演到全纽约居民全死或是全昏迷了，现在我没机会知道后续发展了。

yingyinNormal.en: So I knocked down the bathroom door, picked up my poor unconscious mother, carried her to the car, and drove like a madman to the emergency room.
yingyinNormal.zh: 于是我撞开了洗手间的门，抬起我那不省人事的母亲，把她抱上车，然后像个疯子一样开来了急诊室。
